      { id: 'D', text: 'Configure Amazon Route 53 to point to AWS Global Accelerator. Configure Global Accelerator to point to API Gateway API endpoint(s) of both regions via an Application Load Balancer(ALB). Configure the APIs to forward requests to an AWS Lambda function in the respective Regions. Setup the Lambda function to retrieve and update the data in a DynamoDB global table' }
