    stem: 'The DevOps team for an e-commerce company wants to implement a patching plan on AWS Cloud for a large mixed fleet of Windows and Linux servers. The patching plan has to be auditable and must be implemented securely to ensure compliance with the company\'s business requirements. Which of the following options would you recommend to address these requirements with MINIMAL effort? (Select two)',
